nd 16-5 required proof format debugging rather than a simple pass.\n   744→\n   745→## 4. What Went Well\n   746→\n   747→- **2 stories completed, 0 failures, 0 skips.** Clean session with no rework loops.\n   748→- **16-6 full lifecycle in a single session.** backlog to done with no issues — the BMAD workflow update was straightforward.\n   749→- **Epic 16 at 75% completion (6/8).** Steady progress; only docs (16-7) and test updates (16-8) remain."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01WKb4pPG6PLuxxxnWVqC91B","session_id":"4e7b67ce-a5dd-4961-be94-794643eae587","uuid":"53784e22-9f96-4210-845c-5fa285b46a49","timestamp":"2026-03-27T14:26:23.783Z"}
