{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01GAgVNWCcyLJBKVDxD7utPu","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"```\n[OK] Session retrospective complete\n```\n\n## Summary\n\nAll 74 stories across 16 epics are **done**. No actionable work remains.\n\nThis session's only work was fixing state corruption for the **4th time today** — ralph's state reconciliation keeps resetting `done` stories to `review` by ignoring git commits and proof documents. This is a known bug (story 11-3's reconciliation code) that has been flagged in 7 consecutive retrospectives.\n\n**Two critical fixes needed before the next sprint:**\n1. Guard `done` as an immutable terminal state in reconciliation — never reset a story that has a committed proof document\n2. Add ralph session termination when sprint is 100% complete — stop spawning sessions that have nothing to do\n\n```\nAll sprint work complete. Consider running /sprint-planning for the next sprint.\n```"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1510,"cache_read_input_tokens":60363,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1510},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4e7b67ce-a5dd-4961-be94-794643eae587","uuid":"e45d62dc-d394-4b40-aaf8-f011964f5410"}
